Cocchetto Solutions Inc is a family run business that we have been servicing the Woodstock, Ingersoll and surrounding area since 2008.
We offer renovations, new build, and carpentry services in the residential and commercial sector. As a family company we strive on communication, excellence and quality to help you bring your dream, imagination to life.
Here are some services we offer are Decks, Fences, Garages, Additions, Drywall, Painting, Framing, Finishing, General Maintenance, etc 
Please give use a call and we will be happy to give a quote on your project.
“We have the solution to your problem” 
Thanks Cocchetto Solutions Inc Family
